{"tid":13924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失蹤前曾搵跳崖地點　IT男伏屍山頂崖底","createTime":"2016-11-30T09:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T05:22:37.000Z","uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"089b9cd3ea31931d27ac3b9b90fad5f3d276f05d","tid":13924,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:37:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161130/55985060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161130%2F55985060&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=4ba009e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161130%2F55985060&h=99332fb8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161130/55985060</a><br />\n<br />\n失蹤前曾搵跳崖地點 IT男伏屍山頂崖底<br />\n<br />\n【17:28 更新】死者何偉健生前曾任職資訊科技(I.T.)人員，失蹤前在家中電腦搜尋跳崖資料<br />\n<br />\n【16:40】消防處稱，下午3時49分救援人員在懸崖底、離地約15米找到一具男性屍體，現正設法將他抬上地面。<br />\n<br />\n【15:47】懷疑墮坡事主，為失蹤個半月的47歲男子何偉健。<br />\n<br />\n47歲男子何偉健失蹤近個半月，港島總區失蹤人口調查組追尋多日，憑閉路電視畫面，鎖定事主最後於山頂出現，今早上山搜索，及至中午在柯士甸山道發射站發現事主的背囊，懷疑事主墮下山坡，於是通知消防及飛行服務隊協助搜索。至下午3時49分，救援人員在懸崖底、離地約15米找到一具何的屍體，稍後會將遺體抬上地面。<br />\n<br />\n死者何偉健生前曾任職資訊科技(I.T.)人員，本身有抑鬱症，有自殺傾向。他上月20日離開油麻地彌敦道寓所後失蹤(<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2gEL7nn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2gEL7nn&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=cbdbbf33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2gEL7nn</a>)。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，何妻在丈夫的電腦內，發現丈夫曾上網搜尋跳崖地點，通知警方。警方接手跟進，翻查何有機會出沒地點的閉路電視錄影，終鎖定目標，今午在上址尋獲何的屍體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前世做錯事<br />\n今世做IT :("},{"pid":"92b3e89cf67d8eaa744f98fd0c401ebcbcdc9a69","tid":13924,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131f0ba5c7280064c6aa6fd3a3a7cd9bd75b8285","tid":13924,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:42:37.000Z","msg":"47歲(跳崖自殺)"},{"pid":"78400874f09dae9a6d30d5bbd95871f3ac4f1e6e","tid":13924,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394ad910c904f02dda298d9258e0a1bb85783285","tid":13924,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>47歲(跳崖自殺)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba27e54d35d23a762e45c810786b4b0e532db537","tid":13924,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>47歲(跳崖自殺)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n47歲(IT狗)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d85f9ce805af492dcbacb44a969e731f17ecd3","tid":13924,"uid":18988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9983f732e5545b9c8b2cc730a1a766a3296986a1","tid":13924,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:54:34.000Z","msg":"rest in python"},{"pid":"c166fd1e5d27a8ac1ba442e9c737615616166217","tid":13924,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:54:44.000Z","msg":"rest in php"},{"pid":"8b301a617f5781f3c550cfe7fbfadee55dc7fd4d","tid":13924,"uid":6076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:55:19.000Z","msg":"47歲男子何偉健失蹤近個半月，港島總區失蹤人口調查組追尋多日，憑閉路電視畫面，鎖定事主最後於山頂出現，今早上山搜索，及至中午在柯士甸山道發射站發現事主的背囊，懷疑事主墮下山坡，於是通知消防及飛行服務隊協助搜索。至下午3時49分，救援人員在懸崖底、離地約15米找到<span style=\"color: red;\">一具何的屍體</span>，稍後會將遺體抬上地面。<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野中文 講到好似有第二具咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffd1dc4860cdf2023ec2025f6b83709ebd34ac5","tid":13924,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:56:58.000Z","msg":"it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8054a359e7bf1ea2aee385000cd17daa544ecbde","tid":13924,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5178278638297c803ba73c40314c284fb3616456","tid":13924,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>rest in php</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nredt in prolog"},{"pid":"3a803197d01384aa88192f21db5445898cc2e823","tid":13924,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"腦魔仲未入黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536cbff84d6f60e2b667791253776f1b67c51f2c","tid":13924,"uid":14091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:21:19.000Z","msg":"成個topic 最sad係「IT男」<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw RIP"},{"pid":"03c8a37087e53688e2e7b67b626c921f97b6de6e","tid":13924,"uid":28863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:31:40.000Z","msg":"IT狗，rip，我仿佛見到自己最後結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0077d9dd659d1d065b8af1a1ac4f0a1f18046cdb","tid":13924,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T14:59:07.000Z","msg":"Rest In Pascal<br />\n<br />\ngoto hell;"},{"pid":"17c7920ec36cfdebb4df4c48d3f6a5d4b925652c","tid":13924,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14ff3193c2f6aa0ae5f2f64a6f4243baa1718bc0","t